                </div>
              </div>`;
          }
        }

        function critique(data) {
          let lines = [];
          if (data.score >= 80) lines.push('This is a strong headline. It hits most of the key scoring dimensions and should earn above-average click-through rates.');
          else if (data.score >= 60) lines.push('This headline is solid but has room for improvement. A few targeted tweaks can lift the score significantly.');
          else lines.push('This headline is underperforming. It is missing several elements that drive clicks in search and social.');
          if (data.dimensions['Length'] < 12) lines.push('Work on the length so it does not get truncated or look too thin in the SERP.');
          if (data.dimensions['Power Words'] < 5) lines.push('Add a power word to trigger emotion or urgency.');
          if (data.dimensions['SEO Strength'] < 10) lines.push('Use a number, question word, or list format to strengthen SEO signals.');
          if (data.dimensions['Local SEO'] < 5 && cityEl.value) lines.push('Your city or industry keyword is not showing up in the headline; adding it will improve local relevance.');
          return lines.join('\n\n');
        }

        function generateRewrites(headline, keyword, city, industry) {
          const k = keyword || 'your keyword';
          const c = city ? city.split(',')[0] : '';
          const ind = industry ? industry.replace('_', ' ') : '';
          const year = new Date().getFullYear();
          const templates = [
            { t: `7 ${k.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + k.slice(1)} Tips That Actually Work${c ? ' in ' + c : ''}`, reason: 'Adds a number and a promise, which lifts CTR.', type: 'Listicle' },
            { t: `How to ${k.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + k.slice(1)}${c ? ' in ' + c : ''}: The ${year} Guide`, reason: 'How-to format with year marker signals fresh, comprehensive content.', type: 'How-to' },
            { t: `Why ${k.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + k.slice(1)} Matters More Than Ever${c ? ' in ' + c : ''}`, reason: 'Question-style angle creates curiosity.', type: 'Question' },
            { t: `${c ? 'Best ' + ind + ' in ' + c : 'Best ' + k + ' in ' + year + ': Top Picks Reviewed'}`, reason: 'Superlative + local/year combo targets high-intent searches.', type: 'Superlative' },
            { t: `Limited: ${k.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + k.slice(1)} Offer${c ? ' for ' + c : ''} This Month`, reason: 'Urgency and scarcity drive immediate clicks.', type: 'Urgency' },
          ];
          return templates.map((item, i) => {
            const mock = analyze(item.t);
            return { ...item, score: mock.score, grade: grade(mock.score) };
          });
        }

        function renderRewrites(rewrites) {
          const card = document.getElementById('ha-rewrites-card');
          const box = document.getElementById('ha-rewrites-content');
          card.classList.remove('ha-hidden');
          box.innerHTML = rewrites.map((r, i) => `
